metadata.title: Madrona Brands Pineapple Windsock - Durable Outdoor Yard Decoration for Yard, Garden, Patio, Beach and More 42-Inch
features: Madrona Brands Pineapple Windsock will bring a smile to your face with it’s cheerful and fun design. Great for those that want to decorate their outdoor spaces with an eye-catching windsock design.

This windsock is 42 inches long and made of high-quality polyester fabric and sewn tail edges that are weather resistant for longer lasting enjoyment all season long. The design is a pattern of bright pineapple with green leaves on top and includes 6 tails to catch the breeze.
Hang anytime of year on patios, decks, porches and more. It makes a great gift or welcome seasonal decor around an entryway.
Ready to hang upon arrival with no assembly required. Includes a metal, swivel hanging clip that allows it to spin freely and collapses down to easily store away flat when needed.
Enjoy watching nature in motion as this pineapple dances and spins in the breeze. See our other great windsocks at Madrona Brands Amazon store.
description: This Madrona Brands Pineapple Windsock brings a fun and cute design of happiness and cheer to your outdoor decor. At 42 inches long and made of high-quality polyester fabric and sewn edges this outdoor decoration will last you for years of fun. Hanging this is easy with the included metal clip. This decoration flows beautifully in the breeze and makes for a great outdoor decoration around your home or place of business.  ★ Quality Material: Made of high-quality polyester fabric.  ★ Hang Anywhere: These can easily be hung from just about anywhere with the included metal clip, no pole or extra brackets required.  ★ Classic Decoration: Add a pop of color and fun to your outdoor spaces, backyards, and more. Enjoy Amazon's fast delivery!
